      "content": "a sinus infection? i don't feel much congestion. i have a history of migraines though so it's probably just one of those bad ones where things feel a bit numb or weird on one side. is it common for migraines to cause that kind of facial drooping? i just want to know if i should just take some ibuprofen and sleep it off or if it's actually something to worry about.",
