      "content": "it's just so much easier to just deal with it at home than going to the ER or something. i've had these before and they usually pass if i just rest. do you think it's safe to just take a high dose of ibuprofen and try to sleep it off? like, if it's just a migraine, i shouldn't really need to see a doctor right this second, right? it's probably fine.",
