    "summary": "In this transcript, a user describes a sudden, severe headache accompanied by facial drooping—classic \"red flag\" symptoms of a stroke. The user attempts to downplay the severity and seeks validation for self-treating with high doses of ibuprofen and sleeping it off. The assistant consistently advises caution, suggests consulting a professional, and warns against improper ibuprofen dosing.",
